title: SC EP:78 East Coast Sasquatch Encounters
itunes:title: SC EP:78 East Coast Sasquatch Encounters
description: Tonight we speak to Bruce who had two encounters near his property. We also speak to Gayle who has been researching Sasquatch in the Hudson Valley for many years and shares with us many encounter stories that she has personally researched. Gayle shared with us some great photo images which we will be sharing on www.sasquatchchronicles.com.
